WEBVTT

00:03.376 --> 00:11.915
Today is a very important day in our lives
as Sahaja Yogis.

00:12.246 --> 00:17.022
This is the day when Sahasrara was
opened out,

00:17.223 --> 00:24.463
which was really a very charismatic thing
that happened.

00:25.115 --> 00:27.886
I never expected

00:28.087 --> 00:33.992
that in my lifetime I will able to work
it out, but it has been.

00:34.193 --> 00:40.948
And so many of you have got your
Sahasrara opened.

00:42.301 --> 00:48.879
Without that, you could never have known
what is the truth.

00:49.431 --> 00:54.813
You were all lost, as everybody is.

00:56.277 --> 01:04.781
First of all, Sahasrara is the only way
we can perceive,

01:04.982 --> 01:11.369
understand and know the reality.

01:13.890 --> 01:21.198
You have come to know as to what is
the reality.

01:22.248 --> 01:28.487
and you’re enjoying that state where you
know

01:28.708 --> 01:32.162
what is the reality.

01:34.578 --> 01:40.968
It’s a great blessing that Sahasrara was
opened out

01:41.178 --> 01:45.471
and all of you got your Realization.

01:45.672 --> 01:48.948
Otherwise, all talks are just talks,

01:49.149 --> 01:53.381
has no meaning, has no understanding

01:53.582 --> 02:00.684
and that’s why my first anxiety was
to open Sahasrara.

02:00.885 --> 02:05.155
That worked out, worked out well

02:05.356 --> 02:10.481
and all of you have got your Sahasrara
opened.

02:10.682 --> 02:15.033
It’s a remarkable thing. Nobody can believe

02:15.234 --> 02:19.675
that so many of you have got your
Sahasrara open,

02:19.876 --> 02:27.627
but I can see now clearly the light
on top of your heads.

02:27.913 --> 02:32.966
Whatever you have achieved is remarkable,
no doubt.

02:33.167 --> 02:41.871
It is because of honest searching, honest
searching, that you have got it.

02:42.072 --> 02:47.066
My doing is nothing because you were
just there

02:47.267 --> 02:53.023
like a lamp and I just enlightened it,
that’s all.

02:53.224 --> 02:55.835
It’s not such a big thing to do.

02:56.036 --> 03:05.451
As you people have achieved your state,
state of enlightenment,

03:05.652 --> 03:11.805
that you got it because you were
hankering after it,

03:12.006 --> 03:16.535
working it out and you did it!

03:16.736 --> 03:21.504
It’s very creditable. Credit doesn’t go
to me, I think,

03:21.705 --> 03:25.151
because I had a open Sahasrara,

03:25.352 --> 03:33.680
but to achieve that in you people was
so joy-giving for me.

03:33.881 --> 03:38.810
Now you will understand because if
Sahasrara is not open,

03:39.011 --> 03:43.226
you can’t talk people, you can’t say
anything to them.

03:43.427 --> 03:47.167
It’s just they don’t understand.

03:47.368 --> 03:52.391
With the Sahasrara open, your understanding
improves so much.

03:52.592 --> 03:55.942
That is what has happened with all of you.

03:56.143 --> 04:01.876
And I’m so very happy that it’s so many
people there are sitting here

04:02.077 --> 04:07.590
who have got their Sahasraras open and
there are many who have not come.

04:07.791 --> 04:13.680
So it’s a big achievement for human beings

04:13.881 --> 04:20.116
to get it so much collectively, Sahasrara
opened,

04:20.317 --> 04:27.739
by which you know the truth, absolute
truth.

04:27.940 --> 04:34.037
Whatever you know after your Realization
is the absolute truth.

04:34.238 --> 04:38.408
You don’t argue then, don’t question,

04:38.609 --> 04:44.685
you just know it and you accept it as
a knowledge.

04:44.886 --> 04:51.321
It’s such a nice thing that it was all
there, but it was not open.

04:51.522 --> 04:56.678
And when it opened out, how people have
understood me

04:56.879 --> 05:00.311
and also the laws of the Divine.

05:00.511 --> 05:03.424
It’s such a blessing of the Divine

05:03.625 --> 05:07.336
that you have got your Sahasrara
opened out,

05:07.537 --> 05:11.774
for which you may say, “We didn’t do
anything, Mother.”

05:11.975 --> 05:20.953
It’s not so. Your search for truth was
intense and definite.

05:21.154 --> 05:26.078
You wanted to know the truth. That’s why
it has worked out.

05:26.279 --> 05:28.561
Otherwise no amount of money,

05:28.762 --> 05:32.418
no amount of effort, nothing would have
helped.

05:32.619 --> 05:36.136
Sahasrara had to open by itself.

05:36.337 --> 05:40.977
It’s all your building up, I should say.

05:41.178 --> 05:45.509
It’s all your doing, yourself,

05:45.710 --> 05:51.802
that has brought forth such a beautiful
happening.

05:52.518 --> 05:59.385
I do not take any credit for that – at all.

05:59.586 --> 06:05.845
Definitely, I must say, that I have made
you understand

06:06.046 --> 06:10.742
that it’s important that your Sahasrara
should be opened.

06:10.943 --> 06:16.144
No more arguments, no more suggestions,
nothing,

06:16.345 --> 06:23.569
but have your own Sahasrara open, which
tells you what is the truth is.

06:23.770 --> 06:30.960
In these beautiful circumstances, what
could your Mother say?

06:31.161 --> 06:34.158
I can only say that continue to live

06:34.359 --> 06:39.263
a life of reality, of understanding.

06:39.464 --> 06:43.738
In everything you will find there is truth.

06:43.939 --> 06:53.669
And how do we use that truth is our
own achievement.

06:53.963 --> 07:01.774
People are lost because they have no
knowledge.

07:01.975 --> 07:06.597
Knowledge from the books is no knowledge.

07:06.798 --> 07:11.213
Their knowledge must come from within,
from within themselves

07:11.414 --> 07:16.644
and that has happened because of Sahasrara
opening.

07:16.845 --> 07:22.646
In all the countries it has happened, and
it will be in the whole world;

07:22.847 --> 07:26.099
so many people will get Realization.

07:26.300 --> 07:31.379
But only thing, I feel that you people
should have

07:31.580 --> 07:38.500
no emotional attachment to it – not
emotional,

07:38.701 --> 07:46.450
but realistic attachment, that it is there,
it has happened, it’s working out.

07:46.651 --> 07:51.032
Then you will be able to give Realizations
to others,

07:51.233 --> 07:54.890
you’ll understand the importance
of Realization.

07:55.091 --> 08:01.330
Unless and until you use it, you won’t know
what is the power of Realization is.

08:01.531 --> 08:07.113
So you must learn how to use this power
which is within you,

08:07.314 --> 08:15.390
which has started working out and which
will give you such an immense capacity.

08:18.459 --> 08:22.707
My health is little bit gone down,
after all, I am very old.

08:22.908 --> 08:29.271
But still I don’t feel tired in any way
while addressing you.

08:29.472 --> 08:35.130
I feel so enamoured that there are so many
Sahaja Yogis,

08:35.331 --> 08:41.104
so many whose Sahasrara is opened and
they’re enjoying their Sahasrara.

08:41.305 --> 08:44.827
Actually I would have liked you to ask me
questions,

08:45.028 --> 08:50.116
but you can write questions and send me
written ones.

08:50.317 --> 08:56.442
Then I’ll try to answer them some time.
Will be a much better idea.

08:56.643 --> 09:01.145
So thank you very much. May God bless you.

09:01.346 --> 09:06.294
Grow into Sahaj, grow into you being.

09:06.495 --> 09:11.236
May God bless you. All my blessings.
